### Login de usuário

POST http://localhost:3000/user/login HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "leon@test.com",
  "password": "senhasegura"
}

### criando um usuario completo com SENHA
POST http://localhost:3000/user/ HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "LEONARDO NQUARESMA",
  "cpf": "12345672200",
  "email": "leon@test.com",
  "password": "senhasegura",
  "type": "ADMIN",
  "status": "ATIVO",
  "birthDate": "1995-05-10T00:00:00.000Z"
}

### TESTE DE ERRO 1: Criando usuário com TIPO INEXISTENTE (TEACHER)
POST https://uc13-projeto-2xiu.onrender.com/user/ HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Kevin Valido",
  "cpf": "12345678911",
  "email": "kevin@email.com",
  "type": "TEACHER",
  "status": "INATIVO",
  "birthDate": "2005-05-10T00:00:00.000Z"
}

### TESTE DE ERRO 2: Criando usuário com NOME SENDO NÚMERO (Inválido)
POST https://uc13-projeto-2xiu.onrender.com/user/ HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": 12345,
  "cpf": "12345678911",
  "email": "kevin@email.com",
  "type": "ADMIN",
  "status": "ATIVO"
}

### TESTE DE ERRO 3: Criando usuário com NOME COM LETRAS INSUFICIENTES OU CARACTERES ESPECIAIS
POST https://uc13-projeto-2xiu.onrender.com/user/ HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "A_",
  "cpf": "12345678911",
  "email": "kevin@email.com",
  "type": "ADMIN",
  "status": "ATIVO"
}

### TESTE DE ERRO 4: Criando usuário com CPF CONTENDO LETRAS E TAMANHO ERRADO
POST https://uc13-projeto-2xiu.onrender.com/user/ HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Maria Teste",
  "cpf": "123456789A",
  "email": "maria@email.com",
  "type": "ADMIN",
  "status": "ATIVO"
}

### TESTE DE ERRO 5: Criando usuário com EMAIL INCORRETO
POST https://uc13-projeto-2xiu.onrender.com/user/ HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Maria Teste",
  "cpf": "12345678999",
  "email": "maria_sem_arroba.com",
  "type": "ADMIN",
  "status": "ATIVO"
}

### TESTE DE ERRO 6: Criando usuário com CAMPOS DESCONHECIDOS (Ativará o STRICT do schema)
POST https://uc13-projeto-2xiu.onrender.com/user/ HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Hackerzin",
  "cpf": "12345678911",
  "email": "hackerzin@email.com",
  "type": "ADMIN",
  "status": "ATIVO",
  "campoImpossivel": "MudarPermissaoDireto"
}

### TESTE DE ERRO 7: Criando usuário com DATA DE NASCIMENTO NO FUTURO
POST https://uc13-projeto-2xiu.onrender.com/user/ HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Fulano Viajante do Tempo",
  "cpf": "12345678911",
  "email": "futuro@email.com",
  "birthDate": "2050-05-10T00:00:00.000Z"
}

### TESTE DE ERRO 8: Criando usuário com NOME GIGANTE (+100 Caracteres)
POST https://uc13-projeto-2xiu.onrender.com/user/ HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Este Nome E Extremamente Longo E Passa Dos Limites Permitidos Pelo Banco De Dados Entao O Zod Deve Bloquear Porque Isso Nao Pode Acontecer De Jeito Nenhum Com Centenas De Caracteres",
  "cpf": "12345678911",
  "email": "longo@email.com"
}


### Listar todos os usuários
GET https://uc13-projeto-2xiu.onrender.com/user/ HTTP/1.1
content-type:aplication.json

### Filtrar pelo atributo nome
GET https://uc13-projeto-2xiu.onrender.com/user?name=Vanessa HTTP/1.1
content-type:aplication.json

### Filtrar pelo status
GET https://uc13-projeto-2xiu.onrender.com/user?status=ATIVO HTTP/1.1
content-type:aplication.json

### Filtrar pelo tipo "TEACHER"
GET https://uc13-projeto-2xiu.onrender.com/user?type=TEACHER HTTP/1.1  
content-type:aplication.json

### Filtrar pelo tipo "ADMIN"
GET https://uc13-projeto-2xiu.onrender.com/user?type=ADMIN HTTP/1.1
content-type:aplication.json

### Mostrar um único usuário
GET https://uc13-projeto-2xiu.onrender.com/user/2 HTTP/1.1 
content-type:aplication.json

### Listar usuários nascidos entre 1990 e 2000
GET https://uc13-projeto-2xiu.onrender.com/user?birth_min=1990-01-01&birth_max=2000-12-31 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

### Mostrar o usuário que eu quero editar
PUT https://uc13-projeto-2xiu.onrender.com/user/2 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Lucas",
  "email": "lucas@email.com",
  "birthDate": "2006-05-10T00:00:00.000Z"
}

### Deletar o usuário
DELETE https://uc13-projeto-2xiu.onrender.com/user/1 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

